name: Occasion Cards
description:
This includes:

-5 thank you cards
-2 happy anniversary cards
-2 congratulations cards
-2 i love you cards
-3 happy birthday cards
-1 hello. card

....a total of 15 uniquely designed cards set in calligraphy!

Only $2.00 per card when you break it down...much better than your box store price ;)

Fun to have on hand for every occasion!

name: Envelope Addressing
description:
This listing is per envelope:
-black ink on white envelopes (with no envelope liner)
-with Copperplate Script
-staggered address

*For colored, white or gray ink please add this listing, plus "Envelope Addressing, colored ink" to your cart

**For black or colored ink on a colored envelope, please purchase this listing plus "Envelope Addressing, colored envelope"

***For centered address, please purchase "Envelope Addressing, center addressing" along with this listing.

name: Wedding Vows
description:
This is for a set of 2 vows on acid-free paper!

Your special day is amazing, and so are the vows that you're now living out!  
It's so fun to give these as a gift to your spouse for your anniversary or valentine's day...or just because.

And it's so great to be able to read through them and be reminded of the special promises you have for each other.

This is in Copperplate Script with black ink.

name: Place Card Calligraphy
description:

If you want another color ink please purchase the "place card colored ink"
